column3: Congratulations! You’ve won a $500 gift card to Target. Click here to claim your reward.
Hello John, your shipment from UPS will arrive today. Click here to track your package
Your Wells Fargo account has been locked for suspicious activity. Please log in here and verify your account.
Hey, this is Jill. I’m in a meeting, but I need you to order 5 Amazon gift cards ASAP. I’ll reimburse you once you send them to this email address.
Jack, your Verizon billing statement is ready. Please review your charges and send full payment by [date] to avoid late fees.
Damn. Hospital politics are the worst
